DESCRIPTION:Just a gentle reminder\, payroll timesheets are due\, at the en
 d of your workweek\, and no later than Monday by noon. otherwise\, you wil
 l have to wait until the next pay period to get paid. \nPlease remember to
  complete your timesheet on Gulfline.\nThank you\n\n\nRichard Santiago \nF
 lorida Gulf Coast University\nInformation Technology Services \nHelpdesk S
 upervisor\n10501 FGCU Boulevard South \nFt Myers\, FL 33965-6565 \nOffice 
        (239) 590-7103\nCell             (239) 823-8085 \nrsantiag@fgcu.edu
  \n  \n  \nInformation Technology Services will never ask for your passwor
 d.\nhttps://www.fgcu.edu/techservices/\n\nFlorida has a very broad public 
 records law.  As a result\, any written communication created or received 
 by Florida Gulf Coast University employees is subject to disclosure to the
  public and the media\, upon request\, unless otherwise exempt.  Under Flo
 rida law\, e-mail addresses are public records.  If you do not want your e
 mail address released in response to a public records request\, do not sen
 d electronic mail to this entity.  Instead\, contact this office by phone 
 or in writing.\n\n\n\n\n
