DESCRIPTION:More info to come\n\n\n\n\n\nHello John\,\n\nI hope you’re do
 ing well! I’m reaching out to see if you could assist with the execution
  of this year’s MLK Celebration Dinner\, which will take place on Tuesda
 y\, January 21st\, from 7:00–9:00 PM.\n\nThis year\, we’re planning to
  incorporate mini skits during the program\, and I would greatly appreciat
 e your support with the ITS portion to ensure everything runs smoothly.\n\
 nPlease let me know if you’d be able to assist with this\, and feel free
  to reach out if you need any additional details.\n\nThank you so much for
  your time and expertise!\n\nBest regards\,\nT.O.\n\n
