DESCRIPTION:Add small giga switch so Joel can stream.  Take a long cable or
  two\n\n\n\nHi John\,\n\nThank you for the call back today to figure out t
 he ilvestream for the FGCU Storytelling events this semester with the Dept
  of Lang & Lit.\n\nWe will need an extra ethernet port to connect a comput
 er for livestreaming since the wifi is too slow. The ethernet switch that 
 you suggested would be perfect to plug into for the events this semester.\
 n\nI would like to test the ethernet connection for livestreaming next Tue
 sday Sep 16 at 11:30am in the art gallery.\nIf you can have an active ethe
 rnet port there to plug into that would be awesome.\n(I'm flexible on Tues
 day between 11am - 2pm and Thursday between 11am - 2pm if that time does n
 ot work out.)\n\nThank you\,\nJoel\n\n
