DESCRIPTION:Good morning\,\n\nAs per the email below you have not received 
 a request I submitted in the recent weeks for IT support for the EA Recept
 ion. Details below.\n\n\n  *   Thursday\, September 18th\n  *   5:00-6:30 
 pm\n  *   Cohen Ball Room\n  *   Microphone\, Power Point on screens\, and
  music during reception\n\nWhat do you need from my end to ensure we have 
 the support necessary for this event? The program\, headed by President Ti
 mur\, will run from 5:30-6pm. I included my cell phone number\, the day of
  the event I will be away from my desk.\n\nThanks\,\nMarilyn\n305-297-1499
 \n\nFrom: Bigos\, Teri <tbigos@fgcu.edu>\nSent: Friday\, September 12\, 20
 25 10:39 AM\nTo: Morejon-McGovern\, Marilyn <mmorejonmcgovern@fgcu.edu>\nC
