 rilyn\,\n\nWe just had our weekly meeting with our campus service provider
 s. ITS is still reporting they have not received a request for the Eagle A
 dvocacy event next week.\n\nMy email below from last week has the link to 
 request ITS. Because it is so late I might also suggest calling John Wilso
 n and/or John Bledsoe.\n\nOther notes:\n\n  *   Catering and the UPD offic
 er was confirmed this morning.\n  *   Physical plant was not on the call s
 o I could not confirm Precool or Directional Signage but I was copied on t
 he emails Jen sent to Physical Plant last weekend and I think you are good
 . However\, I would suggest following up with Andie Morris for the Directi
 onal Signage. The Precool we can handle day of with WMC if needed.\n  *   
